Package Controller

Class Main

java.lang.Object
Controller.Main
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class Main extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The `Main` class controls the main application functionality. It manages appointments and customers, including listing, adding, updating, and deleting them.
